thread.title: Kendra
thread.title_full: JB Prince Company reviewed by Kendra

author: Kendra
title: Kendra
text: They had an error on their end when it came to where to ship my item and contacted me quickly to confirm. No problems since. Package was shipped in a decent box that fit my item and was protected well with packing paper. Overall good service and the items they have to offer fit my needs.
